\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Common mistakes in upgrade emails\
\pard\pardeftab720\li800\fi-800\ri800\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \uc0\u55357 \u56481  One of the biggest mistakes? Sounding too pushy or desperate. Nobody likes an aggressive nudge. Another one: skipping {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.digistorms.com/blog/jobs-to-be-done-examples"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 personalization}} or sending irrelevant offers. If your trial users or free users can\'92t see how the upgrade improves their specific use case, they\'92ll ignore it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Lastly, avoid overwhelming design or content\'97emails that try to say everything often end up saying nothing. Clarity, timing, and value are key.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 What to include in your upgrade email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Start strong: make your value proposition instantly clear. Highlight what they\'92ll gain\'97features, tools, or support they won\'92t get on the free plan. Add a clear CTA (think \'93Upgrade today\'94 or \'93Choose your paid plan\'94).\
Use simple language, clean layout, and yes\'97social proof if possible. If there\'92s a deadline (like when their trial ends), make that obvious. You want them to decide fast, without confusion.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Upgrade smarter, not harder\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Your goal isn\'92t to flood inboxes\'97it\'92s to send the right message, at the right time, to the right person. Track usage data and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.digistorms.com/blog/email-marketing-for-saas"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 segment users}} based on behavior. Someone who logs in daily? Send a nudge before their trial ends. Someone inactive? Try a reactivation angle.\
Smart upgrade emails aren\'92t louder\'97they\'92re sharper. You\'92ll convert more customers with fewer sends, and fewer complaints about spam.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

